391
00:20:08,080 --> 00:20:09,030
Maybe.

392
00:20:09,200 --> 00:20:10,630
Mr. Du. Don’t touch him.

393
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:11,630
Let him have a rest.

394
00:20:17,480 --> 00:20:18,310
Look,

395
00:20:19,200 --> 00:20:21,270
