535
00:28:32,140 --> 00:28:32,930
Xirui.

536
00:28:32,940 --> 00:28:34,410
-Mr. Shang.
-What are you doing?

537
00:28:34,940 --> 00:28:36,010
Mr. Cheng, I’m sorry to you.

538
00:28:36,940 --> 00:28:37,970
-Mrs. Cao. Mrs. Cheng.
-Mr. Cheng. I’m sorry.

539
00:28:37,980 --> 00:28:39,490
I have

540
00:28:39,500 --> 00:28:41,810
